All Implemented Interfaces:
IPSBinaryLocator, Cloneable
public class PSServerBinaryLocator
extends com.percussion.cms.objectstore.server.PSFieldRetriever
implements IPSBinaryLocator

This class facilitates the locating of binary content through the use of internal Rhythmyx objects and returning the data of that binary content.

PSServerBinaryLocator

public PSServerBinaryLocator(com.percussion.server.PSRequest request,
                             PSLocator locator,
                             String fieldName,
                             long contentTypeId,
                             int childRowId)
Constructs the object.

Parameters:
request - to create an internal request. May be null to use a request for the internal user.
locator - created to locate content items. Must have an id set and a revision. Must not be null.
fieldName - the name of the field containing the binary information. Must not be null or empty.
contentTypeId - the id of the content type containing the field.
childRowId - the row id if the data is to be loaded from a child item, -1 otherwise.
